{"tid":855704,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡雲尼遭尼馬,麥巴比集體欺凌","createTime":"2018-10-10T08:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T05:03:23.000Z","uid":25345,"like":172,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"cfba9ccbfaed7fffb76fb6ea161e8848aae9f052","tid":855704,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2018/10/10/fdf46cb1e72c407ab2e1acac777e1f1e.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2Ffdf46cb1e72c407ab2e1acac777e1f1e.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=fb7042f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國《隊報》的數據稱，尼馬和麥巴比幾乎不傳球給卡雲尼，尼馬200次傳球中只有1次給卡雲尼。<br />\n<br />\n　　今季，巴黎的鋒線三叉戟助他們在法甲取得了創紀錄的9連勝。不過有法國媒體稱，尼馬和麥巴比不想和卡雲尼一起踢球。<br />\n<br />\n　　《隊報》有數據為證，雖然麥巴比和尼馬分居卡雲尼兩側，但尼馬每200次傳球中只有1次傳給卡雲尼，比例僅為0.5%，而麥巴比的傳球中只有5%是給卡雲尼。<br />\n<br />\n　　尼馬25%的傳球給了麥巴比，麥巴比更是有31%的傳球給了尼馬。不管是戰術還是偶然，卡雲尼在鋒線上顯然被孤立了。<br />\n<br />\n　　雖然得不到兩位隊友的支持，卡雲尼依然在6場比賽中攻入5球，尼馬8場8球，麥巴比5場8球，對里昂上演大四喜。"},{"pid":"20d64577073bc7095868e4b394bdf1205030c524","tid":855704,"uid":143768,"like":445,"dislike":1,"score":444,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>　《隊報》有數據為證，雖然麥巴比和尼馬分居卡雲尼兩側，但尼馬每200次傳球中只有1次傳給卡雲尼，比例僅為0.5%，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰0.5% 可能係每次開波個一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d79f20f40ba17935117dddec8d52292bb9861a","tid":855704,"uid":19126,"like":201,"dislike":4,"score":197,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"覺得卡雲尼係烏拉圭打後一格好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9b86143340e8b22a2625404cd0f20a516d0865","tid":855704,"uid":190928,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"更衣室潮文召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e23b9b1ecb92ed4b97a3380e85c8bc2